4.$ conda uninstall pyqt
5.$ conda update conda
6.$ conda update anaconda-navigator or $ conda install anaconda-navigator
7. after successfull install anaconda, type these lines to start your softwares
$ anaconda-navigator 
$ jupyter notebook
$ spyder
